---
title: Sheet Pan Parmesan Chicken with Roasted Green Beans & Garlic Bread
description: Weeknights feeling busier and more jam-packed than ever? We hear you! That’s why we’re bringing you one of our quickest, easiest meals yet. All you have to do is assemble this meal in a sheet pan, pop it in the oven, and dig in! No need to worry about prep or dirtying multiple dishes. This week, we’re featuring crunchy, Parmesan-and-panko-coated chicken, crisp green beans, and garlic butter baguettes—all ready in under 30 minutes. Now that’s a weeknight win.
